    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Cursed Legacy</strong> is an action/exploration game based on “die and retry” and made with love and passion to pay tribute to the games of the 90s. It also offers mini games that give this work an infinite lifespan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 action stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action platformer run'n gun phases</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Metroid-like exploration phases</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save functionality</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Year 3145. The human race has practically disappeared from the universe. The principality of Dallongeville, the last bastion of humanity, no longer exists. It was the scene of the worst abuses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In these tormented times, the young mercenary <strong>Leif</strong> survives by committing the worst misdeeds.  Always in search of power, he will try to steal the <strong>RB209</strong>, in one of the oases of the <strong>Cube god</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you have the courage to accompany him on this odyssey? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/2b70ec0c3ced4c3ef2e71e3ce6cb34e1.poster.avif?t=1750162141\" width=436 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/2b70ec0c3ced4c3ef2e71e3ce6cb34e1.webm?t=1750162141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/2b70ec0c3ced4c3ef2e71e3ce6cb34e1.mp4?t=1750162141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RUN 'N GUN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need some action? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select this mode to only play action phases and master all aspects of the gameplay (rolling, covering, sliding, gravity, etc.).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/461096b2d91e1d0486cc9220f04ce2b4.poster.avif?t=1750162141\" width=434 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/461096b2d91e1d0486cc9220f04ce2b4.webm?t=1750162141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/461096b2d91e1d0486cc9220f04ce2b4.mp4?t=1750162141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORATION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re more of a Metroid-like fan? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select this mode to take control of the RB309 and travel through a large map, searching for upgrades to collect, bosses to defeat and secrets to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/ecda97894e3d1c91a92206f392537f8f.poster.avif?t=1750162141\" width=438 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/ecda97894e3d1c91a92206f392537f8f.webm?t=1750162141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126270/extras/ecda97894e3d1c91a92206f392537f8f.mp4?t=1750162141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MINI GAMES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey, you will find arcade machines to help you make progress through the game. They offer multiple games based on classics like Snake, Minesweeper, Maze crawler and 2048.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
